00:58:34.970 --> 00:58:37.770
to choose yourself over your King?

865
00:58:40.810 --> 00:58:42.210
Your Grace?

866
00:58:43.220 --> 00:58:45.840
I will never recover from Aemma's death.

867
00:58:46.790 --> 00:58:47.980
But Alicent...

868
00:58:48.990 --> 00:58:51.010
she took me

869
00:58:48.990 --> 00:58:51.010
through the worst of my grief.

870
00:58:53.490 --> 00:58:55.480
She was a calculated distraction.

871
00:58:57.360 --> 00:59:00.700
I only now realize

872
00:58:57.360 --> 00:59:00.700
how well-calculated it was.

873
00:59:00.800 --> 00:59:03.030
[Otto] That is an absurdity.

874
00:59:03.640 --> 00:59:05.190
The Queen loves you...

875
00:59:06.840 --> 00:59:08.830
as I know you love her.

876
00:59:08.910 --> 00:59:12.310
Your interests no longer align

877
00:59:08.910 --> 00:59:12.310
with those of the realm.

878
00:59:12.380 --> 00:59:14.740
Your judgment has been compromised.

879
00:59:14.850 --> 00:59:17.340
A loyal Hand must tell his king

880
00:59:17.420 --> 00:59:20.550
a discomforting truth

881
00:59:17.420 --> 00:59:20.550
from time to time. Your Grace.

882
00:59:20.650 --> 00:59:21.810
If he doesn't...

883
00:59:23.660 --> 00:59:25.650
he's failed as a servant.

884
00:59:26.690 --> 00:59:29.060
You were a faithful servant. Otto.

885
00:59:38.670 --> 00:59:40.070
The Crown and the realm

886
00:59:40.670 --> 00:59:43.670
both owe you a debt

887
00:59:40.670 --> 00:59:43.670
that can never be repaid.

888
00:59:44.840 --> 00:59:47.400
But I can no longer trust your judgment.

889
00:59:47.510 --> 00:59:49.070
[somber music playing]

890
01:00:08.270 --> 01:00:09.530
[knock at door]

891
01:00:11.870 --> 01:00:12.960
Come.

892
01:00:17.780 --> 01:00:20.770
I hope you can forgive

893
01:00:17.780 --> 01:00:20.770
the late hour. Princess.

894
01:00:25.650 --> 01:00:28.640
I took great care in its preparation.

895
01:00:31.320 --> 01:00:34.230
If not brewed properly.

896
01:00:31.320 --> 01:00:34.230
it can either prove ineffective

897
01:00:34.290 --> 01:00:38.390
- or else bear unpleasant--

898
01:00:34.290 --> 01:00:38.390
- Brewed properly?

899
01:00:40.230 --> 01:00:41.830
I'm sorry. what is that?

900
01:00:42.570 --> 01:00:44.560
A tea. Princess.

901
01:00:45.170 --> 01:00:46.600
From the King.

902
01:00:47.910 --> 01:00:53.110
It will rid you of any

903
01:00:47.910 --> 01:00:53.110
unwanted consequences.

904
01:00:59.920 --> 01:01:01.350
[door opens]
